      Ŧlibrary file: |.subckt Clarke-abc-Þß-transformation a b c alpha beta\nB1 alpha 0 V=if( flag==0, 2/3 * ( 1*V(a) - 1/2*V(b) - 1/2*V(c) ) , sqrt(2/3) * ( 1*V(a) - 1/2*V(b) - 1/2*V(c) ) )\nB2 beta 0 V=if( flag==0, 2/3 * ( 0*V(a) + sqrt(3)/2*V(b) - sqrt(3)/2*V(c) ) , sqrt(2/3) * ( 0*V(a) + sqrt(3)/2*V(b) - sqrt(3)/2*V(c) ) )\n.ends Clarke-abc-Þß-transformationŧ
